Subject: drm/amdgpu: fix null pointer panic with direct fw loading on gpu reset
Git-commit: 2d4f9020d343a284429eff37ecc9d7e12133da4f
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

When system uses fw direct loading, then psp context structure won't be
initiliazed. And it is also unable to execute mode reset.

